data.description: Large move in ready family home with fenced backyard. Large kitchen with eat-in area and island. Plenty of storage including corner cabinet and closet space with first floor laundry. The first floor features a three quarter bath with tiled flooring and a family room off the kitchen. The dining room has hardwood flooring and glass French doors that lead to a large living room. Added bonus up front is a three season, enclosed front porch. Upstairs you will find a full bathroom, 3 bedrooms and a finished attic. The attic was also used as a bedroom which includes closet space and built in dressers. Many of the windows throughout are updated as well as updated electrical. On a sunny day, enjoy the rear deck and stone outdoor firepit. There is a one stall detached garage as well as a large storage shed in the backyard. Finally, this home is located in a beautiful, quiet neighborhood yet still close to stores and necessities. Call/text today!
